title: Smelling Perfumes While on Day Hike Rest, Setting Up
description: Compound laugh that begins with a belly laugh and then continues to a chuckle. Ella was resting with a dear friend on a long walk in Wilderness Park and brought samples of natural, wild-crafted perfumes for the pair to smell and describe the scents together. This laugh is the first in a series of three clips isolating distinct laughs from the original recording. This laugh occurred while setting up the recording. Ella remembers feeling amused, silly, and charming.
